# Firewall Connectivity Checker (DevSpaces + Prometheus + Auth)

## Run locally
```bash
cd firewall-checker
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
AUTH_MODE=basic BASIC_AUTH_USER=admin BASIC_AUTH_PASS=admin \
python -m uvicorn app.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 3100 --reload
